headline: U.S. Department of Energy’s Office of Technology Commercialization (OTC) Announces Expansion of Quantum-in-Space Collaboration
summary: Honeywell International Inc. (NASDAQ:HON) is one of the Best Quantum Computing Stocks to Buy and Hold for 5 Years. On September 17, the U.S. Department of Energy’s Office of Technology Commercialization (OTC) announced an expansion of Quantum-in-Space Collaboration with 3 new signatories: IonQ, Honeywell International Inc. (NASDAQ:HON), and the Electric Power Board of Chattanooga (EPB). […]
